Basically , each computer that is connected to a network has a specific address known as IP (Internet Protocol) .. It's an address of four numbers seprated with dots : for example :- 192.6.2.272

but as humans it is harder for us to remember the IP so the IP is align with the human readable and rememberable name known as Domain name .. for example :- google.com is the domain name given over the IP 142.250.190.78 and it is easier to search google.com rather than searching with its IP


